title: Cheesy Vegetable Fajitas
ingredients: ['8 flour tortillas', '2 tablespoons vegetable oil', '1 red onion, thinly sliced', '1 green pepper, seeded and sliced into strips', '1 red pepper, seeded and sliced into strips', '1 teaspoon finely chopped garlic', '1 yellow summer squash, halved and sliced into strips', '125g salsa', '1 teaspoon ground cumin', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '115g grated Cheddar cheese', '4 tablespoons chopped fresh coriander']
